data.description: family-friendly living spaces with more than 1,700 square feet in this 2 story Desert View Home 3 bedroom, 2.5 Bath with Loft has a nice size lot this is the home for you!  Has a spaces backyard great for hosting with access to the open kitchen and living area. The spacious Main Living room connects to an open kitchen & dining nook for convenient family gatherings and outside fun.  Upstairs  Loft great for entertaining children or just a nice area to relax!  All bedroom closets have semi walk ins so plenty of storage.  full size laundry room, with a half guest bathroom on main level.  The master suite with a bath & walk-in closet. A full bath is shared by the secondary bedrooms while a half bath is an added convenience for downstairs entertaining.
